<L>__{interior hollywood club (deep) night}
<A>__{at the bar, rusty orders a double. he needs it.}
<C>__{bartender}
<P>__{(shouting over music)}
<D>__{how's the game going?!!}
<C>__{rusty}
<D>__{it's been the longest hour of my life.}
<C>__{bartender}
<D>__{what?!}
<C>__{rusty}
<P>__{(at the same volume)}
<D>__{i'm running away with your wife.}
<A>__{the bartender, not able to hear him, smiles and flashes a thumbs up before moving away.}
<C>__{bartender}
<D>__{cool, man!}
<A>__{behind the bar two go go dancers writhe behind red light district windows, and rusty catches his own fatigued expression in their reflection. then, out the corner of his eye, he catches sight of a man passing through the pulsating crowd. someone familiar to him. he follows.}
